      "text": [
        "198 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «اَلْمَرْأَةُ إِذَا بَلَغَتْ خَمْسِينَ سَنَةً لَمْ تَرَ حُمْرَةً إِلاَّ أَنْ تَكُونَ اِمْرَأَةً مِنْ قُرَيْشٍ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.198 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n'When a woman reaches the age of fifty, She does not see menstruation except if She is a woman from Quraysh.'"
        ]
      }
    },
